      <p><a href="earlyart.shtml">Laying the Ground:&nbsp;The Establishment of an Artistic Milieu in Winnipeg, 1890-1913<br>
      </a><i>by</i> <a href="../../people/davis_ae.shtml">Angela E.&nbsp;Davis</a></p>
      <p><a href="bower_p.shtml">An Interview with Manitoba&rsquo;s New Provincial&nbsp;Archivist, Mr. Peter Bower<br>
      </a><i>by</i> <a href="../../people/babaian_s.shtml">Sharon Babaian</a></p>
      <p><a href="michaels_e.shtml">An Interview with Mr. Emil Michaels<br>
      </a><i>by</i> Stella Hryniuk</p>
      <p><a href="stefansson_v.shtml">Famous Places: Federal Historic Sites in Manitoba<br>
      </a><i>by</i> <a href="../../people/babaian_s.shtml">Sharon Babaian</a></p>
      <p><a href="fortgarrygate.shtml">A Note on the Destruction of Upper Fort Garry<br>
      </a><i>by</i> <a href="../../people/selwood_j.shtml">John Selwood</a></p>
