      </a><i>by</i> John D. Ingram</p>
      <p><a href="photographicworkshop.shtml">Manitoba Photographic Workshop<br>
      </a><i>by</i> Jean Goldie</p>
      <p><a href="mennoniteladies.shtml">From the Ladies Auxiliary to the Mennonite Village Museum, Steinbach,&nbsp;Manitoba<br>
      </a><i>by</i> Jessie Neufeld</p>
      <p><i>The Young Historian: </i><a href="ingram_j.shtml">An Interview with John Ingram: Winnipeg Students Debate History<br>
      </a><i>by</i> <a href="../../people/babaian_s.shtml">Sharon Babaian</a></p>
